        <td colspan="3">
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">The Maximum Contact Shear Stress,Ʈmax, is at a depth below the Cam and Roller Surfaces at about Z = 0.786×b. </para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">You should make sure that the of case hardness depth is a minimum of 1.41×b, even better to make sure it is 2×b</para>
